snippet.title: Sticky Business - Six One Indie Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: Among Us is coming to Sticky Business. Check out the latest Sticky Business trailer to see what's coming in the free update, which brings a collaboration with InnerSloth (the creators of Among Us) to the small business simulation game. The free update features 60 new Among Us-themed stickers, available in 270 color variants. Sticky Business' free Among Us update is coming soon to PC and Nintendo Switch.
